FIRST ADVANTAGE BACKGROUND SERVICES CORP., petitioner,
v.
SUPERIOR COURT OF CALIFORNIA, SAN MATEO COUNTY, et al. No. 18-545. Supreme Court of the United States March 18, 2019.

Motion of Washington Legal Foundation, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeal of California, First Appellate District denied.
